{"tid":602413,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬鞍山女子拋下金銀衣紙後跳樓亡","createTime":"2018-03-23T04:01:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-23T08:17:36.000Z","uid":20933,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"b1aa260c8894d4c068fdc388a4f242a9141deb89","tid":602413,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T04:01:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180323/large/1521774257_bdb8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180323%2Flarge%2F1521774257_bdb8.jpg&h=b2d81cea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n馬鞍山富寶花園，早上9時14分，一名30餘歲女子，從多層停車場的高處墮下，倒臥地下籃球場。救援人員接報到場時，女事主昏迷，立即將她送院搶救，惜告不治。籃球場地上有一包金銀衣紙及一對「人字拖」，停車場4樓的石壆則有一件外套，不排除女事主將金銀衣紙掉落樓後再墮下，警方正調查事主身份及墮樓原因。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288"},{"pid":"80d871b1217e2964bc76af229fe674c7514882b1","tid":602413,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T04:01:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180323/57983774\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180323%2F57983774&d=wZ8Lq8PGBp3%2BE73tT%2F43J54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=89190d27\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180323%2F57983774&h=3f5df943\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180323/57983774</a>"},{"pid":"7c3e0e0e54bdb388249cc44d2f860123e3dd9db0","tid":602413,"uid":74262,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T04:05:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"42a61d03e93818e4c99b1f7f444e8a280342e330","tid":602413,"uid":63950,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":2